        a kūpono no nā keiki, me ka nānā ʻana i nā waiwai mau loa ma mua o ka makaʻu a i ʻole ka hana ʻino.`,

        p7: `❤️ He aha nā waiwai e aʻo ʻia e nā moʻolelo o North Dakota Fairytales?`,
        p8: `ʻImi kēia mau moʻolelo i nā kumuhana honua i hoʻoili ʻia mai kekahi hanauna i kekahi, e like me: ka 
        lokomaikaʻi a me ke aloha, ka maikaʻi a me ka ʻino, ka hoaloha a me ka kūpaʻa, ka koa a me ke kuleana, 
