        nā moʻolelo mālie a piha i ka noʻonoʻo.`,

        p9: `🌍 I nā ʻōlelo hea ka ʻike i loaʻa ai?`,
        p10: `Hana ʻia nā moʻolelo a me nā mele o North Dakota Fairytales i nā ʻōlelo he nui, e like me: English, 
        Spanish, French, Arabic, Russian, Urdu, Hindi, Bengali, Persian, Portuguese, Malay, Indonesian, German, Catalan, 
        Azerbaijani, Armenian, Hawaiian, a me Tatar.
        Kōkua ka haʻi moʻolelo ma nā ʻōlelo he nui i nā keiki e ʻike i nā moʻomeheu like ʻole me ka noho pili mau i nā 
        waiwai kanaka like.`,

        p11: `👶 He palekana anei ʻo North Dakota Fairytales no nā keiki?`,
        p12: `ʻAe. Hana ʻia nā ʻike a pau me ka nānā ʻana i ke olakino manaʻo o nā keiki. ʻO nā moʻolelo: mālie a ʻaʻohe 
        hana ʻino, kūpono no ka ʻohana holoʻokoʻa, a ʻaʻohe mea e hoʻoweliweli ai a i ʻole e hoʻoikaika nui i ka manaʻo. 
        ʻO ka pahuhopu o ka papahana ke hāʻawi i kahi koho mālie i nā pāpaho wikiwiki a walaʻau o kēia au.`,

        p13: `🎶 Ma hea e hiki ai ke nānā a hoʻolohe i nā mea o North Dakota Fairytales?`,
        p14: `Hiki ke loaʻa nā moʻolelo a me nā mele o North Dakota Fairytales ma o: nā puke kiʻi, nā hoʻokuʻu mele, 
        a me nā paepae kikohoʻe. Aia nā loulou kūhelu āpau ma ka pūnaewele.`,

        p15: `🧒 No wai ka makahiki kūpono o North Dakota Fairytales?`,
        p16: `Hoʻolālā ʻia ka ʻike no: nā keiki ʻōpio a me nā ʻohana e makemake ana e heluhelu, hoʻolohe, a kaʻana 
