        p19: `🧾 He ʻoihana anei ʻo North Dakota Fairytales a i ʻole he papahana hana noʻeau?`,
        p20: `He papahana hana noʻeau kūʻokoʻa ʻo North Dakota Fairytales. Hana ʻia nā moʻolelo, nā mele, nā ʻano 
